[SN]TITLE[SN]
Audience appeal for BBC Radio Scotland's Big Debate

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Audience members for Radio Scotland's Big Debate with Gordon Brewer in Ballater are being sought.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The programme is heading to the Deeside town on Friday 11 March from 12:00 to 13:00.
Members of the public interested in joining the audience to discuss the news topics of the week can apply for a ticket.
They should contact bigdebate@bbc.co.uk
